title: EXCLUSIVE: UFO Vs. ARKX Space ETF Battle Reveals 'Only Pure Play' Bet on Sector
description: Since launching in 2019, the Procure Space ETF (NASDAQ:UFO) has positioned itself as the only pure‐play space ETF in the United States, holding a basket of companies with direct exposure to the space industry — a sector that could draw increased attention in 2026 if a potential SpaceX IPO materializes.Procure Holdings CEO Andrew Chanin told Benzinga that maintaining a pure‐play focus is central to the firm's identity and a key differentiator from other space‐themed ETFs.UFO Vs.
